Iʼm Abu Zafar, Lifehacker Video Producer, and This Is How I Work

Iʼm Tim Mulkerin, Lifehacker Social Media Editor, and This Is How I Work

Iʼm Meteorologist Jim Cantore, and This Is How I Work

Iʼm NYX Cosmetics Founder Toni Ko, and This Is How I Work

Iʼm Mark Zuckerman, President of the Century Foundation, and This Is How I
Work

Iʼm McGill Professor Patricia Faison Hewlin, and This Is How I Work

